### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8002
@apiKey = your-api-key-here

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Chat Endpoint - Simple
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "Hola, ¿cómo estás?"
}

### Chat Endpoint - Scientific Query
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "Explica la teoría de la relatividad de Einstein",
  "query_type": "scientific",
  "temperature": 0.1
}

### Chat Endpoint - Creative Query
POST {{baseUrl}}/chat/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "prompt": "Escribe un poema sobre la inteligencia artificial",
  "query_type": "creative",
